{"tid":2250774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12人疑被監視 泛民明質詢保安局","createTime":"2020-10-20T10:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T10:40:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8a618e1bd076cf82558251d26df7eab5497b709e","tid":2250774,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:34:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201020/2LKMTWYMNBDDBPMV6JS6AT5K44/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201020%2F2LKMTWYMNBDDBPMV6JS6AT5K44%2F&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEaDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=bbada963\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201020%2F2LKMTWYMNBDDBPMV6JS6AT5K44%2F&h=3e088b7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201020/2LKMTWYMNBDDBPMV6JS6AT5K44/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n12人疑被監視 泛民明質詢保安局<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dStjnDp-U8fAECytVFxj724mIhI=/1319x1319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z7TFAR4ZU5HDFA4L3KAXMKACS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdStjnDp-U8fAECytVFxj724mIhI%3D%2F1319x1319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ7TFAR4ZU5HDFA4L3KAXMKACS4.jpg&h=18cc6658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■區議員黃永志在中聯辦附近掛上「香港，仲差十二個人」橫額。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12名港人乘快艇涉偷渡到台灣時「被送中」，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇已向立法會呈交關於12港人的口頭質詢，並獲安排於本周三首次大會上提出，保安局需要回應，議案內文則有待立會秘書處跟進。據了解，鄺問題將圍繞當局是否一早知悉12人被送中一事，以及要求盛傳曾監視12人的政府飛行服務隊公開更多相關資料。鄺表示，即使再艱難，亦要設法促使林鄭政府介入事件，令12港人早日平安回港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪促飛行隊按先例公開資料<br />\n<br />\n曾任機師的公民黨議員譚文豪亦會就12港人事件提出書面質詢，當中「踢爆」聲稱不會公開行動細節的飛行服務隊，早於去年11月6日回覆立會議員查詢時曾提供執勤資料，譚要求政府按照該先例，向立會提供多項是次行動資料，包括要求出動飛機的政府部門、飛行服務隊接獲要求日期和時間、機上人員在布袋澳上空執行任務詳情，及機上人員離開布袋澳上空後，在東南方向水域上空執行任務詳情等。<br />\n<br />\n除在立會跟進，。。。。。。。。。。。。。委託律師辯護。<br />\n<br />\n國際社會亦持續關注12港人情況。澳洲工黨參議員Kimberley Kitching昨於facebook張貼手持「#save12HKyouths」標語相片，呼籲世界一定要為香港發聲，並指：「澳洲和香港站在一起。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iKZMh8sJtVk75REtGJyCyicVzUI=/1092x819/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XT6QXMDV2ZGZFIMCVQH6G2FWPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiKZMh8sJtVk75REtGJyCyicVzUI%3D%2F1092x819%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXT6QXMDV2ZGZFIMCVQH6G2FWPQ.jpg&h=67c3b758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄺俊宇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HAmtdyT-ynsOtawSw_s48oYtdE0=/1181x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VAB7WLBHARHKBC5LC3MTJCRHQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHAmtdyT-ynsOtawSw_s48oYtdE0%3D%2F1181x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVAB7WLBHARHKBC5LC3MTJCRHQA.jpg&h=fdbd9dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■澳洲參議員Kimberley Kitching呼籲世界要為12港人發聲。"},{"pid":"85bd93aabb09587606597f23fc0335380945f4e7","tid":2250774,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"香港，仲差十二個人"}]}